    • Class com.envibe.envibe.model.CachedItem extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • purpose

          String purpose
          Describes the service that this item should be associated with. See the static fields of CachedItemDao for valid values.

        • user_tag

          String user_tag
          The user account that this item should be associated with.

        • payload

          String payload
          The payload of data to be stored. Can store any ISerializable or JSON object. May change to be ISerializable instead of String depending on implementation of inherited classes.

    • Class com.envibe.envibe.model.NewsItem extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • post_id

          int post_id
          Unique post ID. Automatically generated by underlying database.

        • username

          String username
          Username of account that created the post.

        • post_date

          Date post_date
          Date and time that the post was written. Should be in UTC time and conversion happens on the frontend.

        • content

          String content
          Content of post. For now is only a generic payload. In the future could be a JSON object with locked-down and pre-validated objects.
